Class TagLockOp

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.impinj.octane.TagOp
      • com.impinj.octane.TagLockOp

  • public class TagLockOp
extends TagOp
    Class to contain the information to perform a tag Lock operation. gen 2 allows a single command to set the lock state of several memory banks
    See Also:
    Gen2 Standard page 88
